subject: Good Day Friend,
body:
Good Day Friend,
I am Chief Accountant/Executive with Foreign Trade Bank of (FTB) . I want to present to you as a beneficiary of $32,640,000 here in my bank. Get back to me for more details.
Best Regards,
Mr. SUN HOR
Account Manager

subject: Re:   Good Day Friend,
body:
Hello Mr. Sun Hor,

Good day to you too! I'm intrigued by your message and would love to hear more about what you have to present from the Foreign Trade Bank. Could you please provide some more details?

Looking forward to hearing from you soon.

Best wishes,
Arthur
